finishedFormEmailText: Thank you for submitting your information to us. We'll be in contact shortly with a quote!

questions.headerText: What types of insurance are you looking for?
questions.subHeaderText: Please select one or both options to start your quote

answers.informationIconText: Auto insurance covers your vehicles and drivers in case of accidents

questions.headerText: What is the address of the home you're insuring?
questions.subHeaderText: Our system can pull information on your home to make this faster

questions.headerText: Can you tell us about the home?
questions.subHeaderText: We need this information to run a quote on your home

questions.headerText: Tell us about the construction of the home
questions.subHeaderText: Please answer these questions to the best of your ability

questions.headerText: Please tell us about the home's location
questions.subHeaderText: This helps us understand the risk of the homes location

questions.headerText: Does your home have a garage?
questions.subHeaderText: Garages can increase the replacement cost of the home

questions.headerText: Can you tell us about the foundation of the home?
questions.subHeaderText: Foundations or basements can increase the replaement cost of the home

questions.headerText: What is your primary source of heating and cooling?
questions.subHeaderText: Please skip this question if you are unsure

answers.placeholderText: Year Heating Last Replaced or Updated

questions.headerText: Are there any fireplaces or wood burning stoves in the home?
questions.subHeaderText: Fireplaces and wood burning stoves can increase the risk of insuring the home

questions.headerText: Are there any pools or trampolines on the premises?
questions.subHeaderText: Pools and trampolines can increase the risk of insuring the home

questions.headerText: Does your home have any dogs?
questions.subHeaderText: This helps us understand if you'll have any pets in the home

questions.headerText: Are there any fine arts, jewlery, guns, or furs stored in the home?
questions.subHeaderText: We can also protect these items in case of a catastrophe

questions.headerText: Is there business conducted in this home?
questions.subHeaderText: We want to make sure our policies provide the right protection

answers.placeholderText: Number Of Employees Work At Home

questions.headerText: Insured
Where should we send your quote?
questions.subHeaderText: Please fill in both email and phone to receive your quote

questions.headerText: What is your current address?
questions.subHeaderText: This helps us understand where you insurance policy will be located at

questions.headerText: Do your currently have home insurance?
questions.subHeaderText: If so, we can skip a few questions

answers.placeholderText: Home Insurance Cancelled In Last 5 Years?

questions.headerText: Have you had any home losses or claims in the last 5 years?
questions.subHeaderText: This gives us insight into your insurance history

questions.headerText: Do any of the following discounts apply?
questions.subHeaderText: Discounts can help save you money on your insurance

options: Early Quoting Discount (2 weeks prior to issuance)
Been With Current Carrier More Than 5 Years
Live in Gated or Secured Community

questions.headerText: Can you tell us about yourself?
questions.subHeaderText: We need this information to get you an accurate quote

questions.headerText: Please tell us about your spouse?
questions.subHeaderText: This is required if you are married

questions.headerText: Where should we send your quote?
questions.subHeaderText: Please fill in both email and phone to receive your quote

questions.headerText: Can you tell us about the driver?
questions.subHeaderText: We need this information to get you an accurate quote

questions.headerText: Tell us about your licensed driving experience
questions.subHeaderText: If you do not know your license information, you can skip that part

questions.headerText: Add or select a driver

questions.headerText: What's the year, make, and model of the vehicle?
questions.subHeaderText: Enter in the VIN to automatically find the vehicle or select it manually below

questions.headerText: Where is the vehicle primarily parked?

questions.headerText: How is this vehicle primarly used?
questions.subHeaderText: This helps us estimate what your wear and tear will be
